X6 是 AntV 旗下的图编辑引擎，提供了一系列开箱即用的交互组件和简单易用的: X6 is AntV's diagram editing engine, which provides a series of easy-to-use interactive components and node customization capabilities to facilitate the rapid construction of DAG diagrams, ER diagrams, flowcharts and other applications
提供基于低学习成本的 SVG/HTML/CSS 的节点定制能力: Provide customization capability based on easy-learning SVG/HTML/CSS
组件完备，开箱即用: Excellent components out of the box
内置 10+ 图编辑场景的配套扩展，如框选、对齐线、小地图等: Built-in 10+ plugins of diagramming scenes, such as selection, snapline, minimap, etc.
画布、节点、边、属性、工具等均可以通过注册机制自由、灵活扩展: Graph, nodes, edges and tools can be freely and flexibly extended through the registration mechanism
